                        <Font name="Segoe UI" size="16.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Text>
                  <Text layoutX="55.0" layoutY="541.0" strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="Characters are the heart of any visual story. They help the audience connect emotionally with the illustration. A character’s pose, facial expression, costume, and body language all contribute to their personality and mood." textAlignment="JUSTIFY" wrappingWidth="727.7760620117188">
                     <font>
                        <Font name="Segoe UI" size="16.0" />
                     </font>
                  </Text>
